Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈爾法國境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 這是什麼玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是糰子了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼買這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 是你買
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？關我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是前幾天那失敗的賠禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我毫無意義地潛入堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到的勇者遺物不會用還丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後你得天天給我買糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟下不管你不也有份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡幾百年的勇者遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那麼容易用得來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且憑啥我就得為此買糰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我買 請讓我買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我這麼悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這都是席恩的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那小子什麼麻煩事都推給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 現在他一定吃著大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠閒地睡午覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}羅蘭德城 會議室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次事件 您打算怎麼負責
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種說法 對陛下太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}絕不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 恕臣直言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下太樂觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜予屬國艾斯塔布爾的國王和貴族我國的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至為領民生活提供保障
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這種態度才會引起叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算boss登場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他也是為國著想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 您打算如何處理此次叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能盡快應對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼盡快應對…消息傳來才第二天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛軍的根據地和主謀都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策已經備妥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛亂的主謀也已查明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾斯塔布爾前國王的獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾婭·艾恩公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情請收集情報的米蘭·弗洛瓦德上校匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報艾斯塔布爾方的兵力約五萬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經不是叛亂了 是戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領地與艾斯塔布爾鄰接的大人們有可能被戰鬥波及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望諸位暫時在本城內避難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們勢必死守諸位的領地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我們離開領地？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任由你這種人踐踏我們的領地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事決無可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非領地裡有什麼見不得人的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那倒沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 各位也可以留在領地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾的勢力不過五萬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不足為懼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 之後我將率軍一支
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往保衛各領地及鎮壓叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這次事件交由克拉烏·柯洛姆少將負責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德負責情報收集和傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輔佐克拉烏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要這種人的支援…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令 克拉烏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德也聽明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場叛亂 是你策劃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓串通者發動叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將艾斯塔布爾的反羅蘭德勢力一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便以戰爭為口實派兵前往各領地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查反國王派貴族們的不正行徑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是如此 您作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盡自己的本職就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}艾斯塔布爾軍 最前線要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王此時還身在羅蘭德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還在意令尊的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊身為我們的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了換取羅蘭德提出的地位和安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易便出賣了國家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得 讓父王來當叛亂的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民眾會更高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們貴族以及國民 都很仰慕您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是我們新的王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾婭·艾恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭 若是敗了將會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且羅蘭德對艾斯塔布爾人民也施以良政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有必要戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將歷史悠久的艾斯塔布爾從羅蘭德手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家什麼的並不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是人民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣人民真的能過上幸福日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不只是白白流血而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要民眾能過得幸福就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你教給我的嗎 薩拉威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們的勢力還很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以羅蘭德也不敢輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而沒有保證今後能維持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於羅蘭德貴族的惡劣傳聞也不絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若您真心為民著想就要把握時機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這樣說 那就必然沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是為了您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們情願付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都過得快樂 所有人都過得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想創造一個這樣的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎 薩拉威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 我們將和羅蘭德開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回我艾斯塔布爾的獨立權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少將傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs40}克裡亞德伯爵領 城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修斯 敵方兵力是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約八、九千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如弗洛瓦德情報所示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就以最小限度的犧牲拿下這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪兒冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種混戰沒法放大魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 指揮官在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這支軍隊的指揮官嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們艾斯塔布爾的指揮官已經被我殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再行抵抗就殺無赦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血染的紅色手指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「紅指克拉烏」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是羅蘭德的紅指克拉烏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊的紅指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說又戰敗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是我軍的動向完全被人看穿了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早說了 這是魯莽之行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅指克拉烏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說羅蘭德的指揮官叫克拉烏·柯洛姆對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞他盡量不殺我方士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令其不戰而降是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若那就是羅蘭德的戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英雄王席恩·阿斯塔爾的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這場戰爭果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定也是敵方的企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了吞併艾斯塔布爾之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不引起憤怒和怨恨才這樣戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有對策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可示弱 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少將的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已包圍了叛軍根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}艾斯塔布爾軍 最前線要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德必須退兵 並釋放俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不同意以上條件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就每時辰殺一個艾斯塔布爾人民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的信已經送給羅蘭德軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德的英雄王不會對人民見死不救的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事出無奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護您 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我而將人民當做人質嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為民著想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們若戰敗後果不堪設想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰敗國的人民將會遭到何等的欺凌羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人民為人質 難道就不算欺凌人民嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能阻止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是被推上台的傀儡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德的軍隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍的士兵正在進攻艾斯塔布爾的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我軍的士兵全都在此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那是哪裡的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陛下送來的援軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩說全權交由我負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成 是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅指克拉烏竟然會無視人質進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人民為人質還被打敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是死刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不一定戰敗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德以為我們不是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要殺了人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我一人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能讓公主殿下獨自去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬下…也與公主殿下共生死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬下也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你們這句話就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位請活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著 努力讓艾斯塔布爾人民過的幸福一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位憂國憂民的心意感人肺腑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 依鄙人之見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾婭·艾恩公主殿下一人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要補償這次的罪孽似乎略顯不足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裝點艾斯塔布爾一國滅亡悲劇的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然還是悲劇最合適 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是羅蘭德帝國軍上校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭·弗洛瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的士兵全滅了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城堡到底沒那麼容易攻陷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說就算攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會讓羅蘭德士兵進城的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡即將上演悲劇的最後一幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影現形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不能丟下大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家 人民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說還有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼上絕路的艾斯塔布爾失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至開始殺害人質
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩拉威爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了理智的就是您 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而手刃瘋狂的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束這場戰爭的艾斯塔布爾貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩拉威爾·塞伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為救國英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為羅蘭德所接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我軍的動向洩露出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要挾持人質的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是你幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那麼相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本的計劃是娶您為妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篡奪這個國家的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…想創造一個所有人都能過得開心的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜言蜜語是無法操縱世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 您真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德還不至於缺英雄缺到讓這種人當英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是羅蘭德的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩·阿斯塔爾的所作所為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾王自然不齒這種行徑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事完全是我獨斷專行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 和薩拉威爾相勾結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煽動我們發動叛亂的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而王卻看破一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命柯洛姆少將而非我鎮壓叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾王就是這樣的偉人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 正如薩拉威爾先生所言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜言蜜語無法操縱世界也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾婭·艾恩公主殺害人質之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯塔爾王會原諒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好是能瞞天過海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該會原諒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是身為王的器量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟是叛亂的主謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真服了您 柯洛姆少將
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到您來得這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少將？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說他就是紅指克拉烏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據回答…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定是否殺了我 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩果然不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不到那位大人所背負的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒是你沒資格侍奉陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要待在席恩身邊根本不需要什麼資格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那位大人即將走上的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要殺掉諾婭·艾恩殿下和人質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你要阻撓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你能拿我怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了艾斯塔布爾人民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能失去這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德上校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若為了完全支配艾斯塔布爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須殺害人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我來說服他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去說服人民和士兵都服從羅蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起殺害人質降低艾斯塔布爾的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這樣做更為有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在艾斯塔布爾人民之中很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 或許也會有人叱責你是賣國賊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後殺了我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請不要殺害大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請撤兵吧 柯洛姆少將
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…你和你的王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆少將
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻煩您拉我站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾人民一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又讓克拉烏殺了人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 這場戰爭是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有追究弗洛瓦德的罪責
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓克拉烏率軍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了盡可能增加獲救的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是給自己找的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩哥哥你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在圖書上看過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是快要哭的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉絲還是第一次看見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲姐姐從來不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西爾哥哥別說哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是一臉陰笑的嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西爾的確很可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶你要哭嗎 哭嗎哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫不是伊莉絲礙著你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次 下次要哭的時候一定要給我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 你不是來報告萊納和菲莉絲的事的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…狗是萊納 天使是菲莉絲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 禽獸君和完全和諧美少女天使菲莉絲姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖洞的時候挖出個短劍樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎麼回事扔了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就長出龍來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是勇者遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供情報的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於他您很瞭解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉絲 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻煩你立即回萊納他們身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那萊納 今天的份靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糰子糰子糰子糰子糰子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩這…席恩這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止說這麼低級的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:23.51,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}製作：akira 安靜の雲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？重新調查之前那勇者遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:26.85,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}漫遊字幕組\Nhttp://popgo.net/bbs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干 麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正去了也是一堆麻煩事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}忘卻碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是麻煩
